@startuml
actor teacher
participant "操作界面" as UI #DDE6F4#032B57 
database studentcourse  #DDE6F4#032B57  
entity student   #DDE6F4#032B57   
control experiment    #DDE6F4#032B57    
boundary experimentscore     #DDE6F4#032B57     
collections scoreitem      #DDE6F4#032B57      

teacher ->UI :1选择学期\n==\nactivate UI \n|||
UI->studentcourse:2查询哪些学生选了老师的课\n activate studentcourse |||\n
studentcourse->student:3请求学生列表\n activate student |||\n
student-->studentcourse:4返回数据\n deactivate student |||\n
deactivate studentcourse |||\n
UI->experiment:5查询这些课程的实验\n activate experiment |||\n
experiment->experimentscore:6查询实验得分\n activate experimentscore |||\n
experimentscore->scoreitem:7查询得分\n activate scoreitem |||\n
scoreitem -->experimentscore:8返回\n deactivate scoreitem |||\n
experimentscore -->experiment:9返回得分\n deactivate experimentscore |||\n
experiment -->UI:10返回得分列表\n deactivate experiment |||\n
UI -->teacher:11显示数据\n deactivate UI 

@enduml